==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Cæcilian
<hw>C⟦ae⟧*cil"i*an</hw> <pr>(?; 106)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>caecus</ets> blind. So named from the supposed blindness of the
species, the eyes being very minute.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A
limbless amphibian belonging to the order <ord>C⟦ae⟧cili⟦ae⟧</ord> or
<ord>Ophimorpha</ord>. See <er>Ophiomorpha</er>.</def> <altsp>[Written
also <asp>c⟦oe⟧cilian</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>caecum</ent>⟦br⟧

